#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:70
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "आमुख"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:72
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&kontact; is the integrated solution for personal information management. "
#| "It combines the well-known &kde; applications for email, scheduling, "
#| "address book, and notes (&kmail;, &korganizer;, &kaddressbook;, and "
#| "&knotes;) into a single interface. Being based on a true component "
#| "framework &kontact; provides exactly the same functionality as the stand-"
#| "alone applications, and adds more features, by making use of the "
#| "integrated way &kontact; runs the applications as components. Users still "
#| "retain the choice of which applications are run within &kontact; and "
#| "which are run stand-alone."
msgid ""
"&kontact; is the integrated solution for personal information management. It "
"combines the well-known &kde; applications for email, scheduling and address "
"book (&kmail;, &korganizer;, &kaddressbook;) into a single interface. Being "
"based on a true component framework &kontact; provides exactly the same "
"functionality as the stand-alone applications, and adds more features, by "
"making use of the integrated way &kontact; runs the applications as "
"components. Users still retain the choice of which applications are run "
"within &kontact; and which are run stand-alone."
msgstr ""
"&kontact; व्यक्तिगतसूचनाप्रबन्धनस्य एकीकृतसमाधानम् अस्ति। सुप्रसिद्धं &kde; ईमेल, "
"समयनिर्धारण, पतापुस्तिका, टिप्पणी च (&kmail;, &korganizer;, &kaddressbook;, "
"&knotes; च) कृते अनुप्रयोगाः एकस्मिन् अन्तरफलके । सच्चिदानन्दरूपरेखायाः आधारेण &kontact; "
"एकान्त-अनुप्रयोगानाम् इव एव कार्यक्षमतां प्रदाति, अपि च अधिकानि विशेषतानि योजयति, "
"एकीकृत-मार्गस्य उपयोगं कृत्वा &kontact; अनुप्रयोगाः घटकरूपेण चालयति । उपयोक्तारः अद्यापि "
"&kontact; ये च एकान्ते चालिताः भवन्ति।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:80
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "In addition to the functionality of the individual applications &kontact; "
#| "provides a summary view and advanced drag &amp; drop features between "
#| "components."
msgid ""
"In addition to the functionality of the individual applications, &kontact; "
"provides a summary view and advanced drag &amp; drop features between "
"components."
msgstr ""
"व्यक्तिगत-अनुप्रयोगानाम् कार्यक्षमतायाः अतिरिक्तं &kontact; सारांशदृश्यं उन्नतं कर्षणं च "
"प्रदाति &amp; घटकानां मध्ये विशेषताः पातयन्तु।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kontact; Components"
msgstr "&kontact; घटकाः"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kontact; integrates the following applications. See the individual "
"application manuals for details on how to use them. These apply to running "
"them as components inside &kontact; just as well as running them stand-alone."
msgstr ""
"&kontact; निम्नलिखित अनुप्रयोगानाम् एकीकरणं करोति। तेषां उपयोगः कथं करणीयः इति "
"विवरणार्थं व्यक्तिगत-अनुप्रयोग-पुस्तिकाः पश्यन्तु । एते &kontact; यथा तान् एकान्ते चालयति।"

